title: Medium Complete Season 4
description:
Allison Dubois works in the Phoenix District Attorney\&#039;s office. She uses her psychic abilities to help crack criminal cases. Her dreams often give her clues to the whereabouts of missing people, and by touching someone she often gets to see beneath the facade into the person\&#039;s soul. Allison juggles this stressful job with her role as wife and mother of three children, including a daughter who seems to be developing similar powers
